1
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:29,799
(The Long Ballad)

2
00:01:29,799 --> 00:01:32,159
(This is a work of fiction.)

3
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:36,239
(Episode 18)

4
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,959
All right.

5
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:40,799
Stop it.

6
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,400
Aren't you the newly appointed military strategist?

7
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,840
What's the matter?

8
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:47,079
Do you think that since His Highness values you,

9
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,920
you can ride roughshod over us?

10
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,760
We have our own rules in the grasslands.

11
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,120
Even if you're with His Highness,

12
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,239
you can't break the rules either.

13
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,280
What's the matter?

14
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,920
Do you want to join in too?

15
00:01:56,439 --> 00:01:57,519
How about...

16
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,680
Come on. Join us.

17
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,719
Let's drink...

18
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,079
Get lost.

19
00:02:05,799 --> 00:02:07,879
Didn't you hear him? He told you to scram!

20
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,680
- Don't go anywhere. - Just wait.

21
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,840
- Just stay there! - Just wait!

22
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,039
I...

23
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,280
Thank you.

24
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,960
You should wipe your face. Your face is full of it.

25
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,240
Let me help you.

26
00:03:04,879 --> 00:03:06,000
You're so pretty.

27
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:12,080
Drink some of this.

28
00:03:13,759 --> 00:03:14,840
I'm Li Shi Si.

29
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,360
What's your name?

30
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,759
Mimi Guli.

31
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,639
You look different from them.

32
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,120
You're not from the Ashina Tribe, right?

33
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,120
I am...

34
00:03:25,759 --> 00:03:27,639
a slave sent to the Ashina Tribe.

35
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,000
I only have men's clothes here.

36
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,280
Just wear it for now.

37
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,280
I'll get changed.

38
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:58,759
Get changed first.

39
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,240
I'll wait outside.

40
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,639
I'm done.

41
00:04:39,759 --> 00:04:41,050
What are you hiding in your clothes?

42
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,680
I...

43
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,680
I'm sorry.

44
00:05:03,279 --> 00:05:04,360
I...

45
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:05,360
I promise.

46
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,839
I'll never steal again.

47
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:08,050
I won't do it again.

48
00:05:08,759 --> 00:05:10,050
Please don't kick me out.

49
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,319
I can do a lot of things.

50
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,319
Look.

51
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,319
I can clean the place.

52
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:15,279
I know how to cook and do laundry too.

53
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:17,000
I can do anything. Look.

54
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,680
I'm good at what I do.

55
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,079
You don't have to hide things anymore.

56
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:27,279
You get to eat what I eat.

57
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,839
Sleep here tonight.

58
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,959
That's my bed.

59
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,279
I'll be right back.

60
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:38,439
Don't answer when someone calls you.

61
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:46,120
(Xijiao Textile Workshop)

62
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,759
Pick a line with your right hand.

63
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,759
Put your hands together.

64
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,439
Go through the line in the middle.

65
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,319
Pick one more with your left hand.

66
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,560
Very good.

67
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,839
Flip it over.

68
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,560
Do you want to play this?

69
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,720
Li Le Yan.

70
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,720
Are you stupid?

71
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,480
Look at what they're doing.

72
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,240
What are you doing?

73
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,439
Are you trying to make me mad?

74
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:39,839
I'm just trying to untangle it.

75
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,920
If you can't undo it tonight, you can't go to bed!

76
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:45,839
Did God send you to test me?

77
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,040
I'm so furious. Come.

78
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,120
Help her!

79
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,120
- Here. - I really don't understand.

80
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,360
You've been learning this for days.

81
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,920
What did you learn?

82
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,959
Who is it?

83
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,639
Why are you going through my stuff?

84
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:20,759
I'm working.

85
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,879
You did all these?

86
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:32,639
If you don't want others to touch your things,

87
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,960
I won't do it again.

88
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,639
I'm sorry.

89
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:37,090
Please don't kick me out.

90
00:08:38,879 --> 00:08:39,879
That's her!

91
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,159
Li Shi Si.

92
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,330
You can't let this woman stay here.

93
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:46,330
What is going to happen if she can't stay here?

94
00:08:46,330 --> 00:08:47,450
Should I kill her?

95
00:08:47,450 --> 00:08:48,919
What's the point of doing this?

96
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,240
You can just kick her out.

97
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,960
I'm begging you. Don't kick me out.

98
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,960
If I get kicked out,

99
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,679
the wolves will eat me up!

100
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,039
Even if I do get out of here,

101
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,519
if Great Khan finds out that I am a runaway slave,

102
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,919
he'll kill me too.

103
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:02,240
- Don't... - Why do you talk so much nonsense?

104
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,759
- Come on! - No!

105
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,639
You...

106
00:09:08,559 --> 00:09:09,679
Are you a dog?

107
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,879
You go around biting people!

108
00:09:10,879 --> 00:09:11,919
You...

109
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,360
Are you done?

110
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,679
Ashina Sun.

111
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:29,279
Your Highness, can you give this servant to me?

112
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:33,879
You may go.

113
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,000
In this place,

114
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:41,879
randomly taking in people...

115
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:43,759
isn't a good thing.

116
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:46,360
Since I'm here to work for you,

117
00:09:46,559 --> 00:09:48,210
then I'll also manage my people.

118
00:09:48,639 --> 00:09:49,639
Don't you trust me?

119
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,480
Let's go.

120
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:59,039
I got bitten for nothing!

121
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,330
What's wrong?

122
00:10:08,330 --> 00:10:10,000
Did you catch a cold last night?

123
00:10:11,039 --> 00:10:13,279
How about this? I'll get you some horse milk wine.

124
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,759
Wait here.

125
00:10:20,210 --> 00:10:22,450
- Ashina Sun. - Come and catch me!

126
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:26,450
Although you agreed to let Li Shi Si be your military strategist,

127
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:28,090
I advise you to be wary of him a bit.

128
00:10:28,090 --> 00:10:29,120
Don't trust him too much.

129
00:10:30,210 --> 00:10:31,279
Why?

130
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:32,450
We don't know where he came from.

131
00:10:32,450 --> 00:10:33,720
I know who he is.

132
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:35,399
But he's not from the grasslands.

133
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:36,399
He is now.

134
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:38,240
But people from the Central Plain have always been tricky.

135
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:42,840
Ashina Sun.

136
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,159
I don't mean anything by that.

137
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:02,840
Are you all right?

138
00:11:03,440 --> 00:11:04,519
I'm fine.

139
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,879
Here.

140
00:11:05,879 --> 00:11:07,840
Have some hot soup. It's good for you.

141
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,360
Just mine?

142
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,639
What about you?

143
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,480
I'm not hungry yet.

144
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,600
Drink up.

145
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,720
You drink it.

146
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,200
I don't have an appetite.

147
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:22,000
Drink this and go to sleep.

148
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:24,759
Even if that cot is small, make do with it.

149
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,879
There's no need.

150
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,440
I'll just sleep on the floor.

151
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:32,799
You should sleep early.

152
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,480
That's how you'll get better.

153
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,039
Do whatever you want.

154
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,799
But you don't have to be wary of me.

155
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:42,320
I won't hurt you.

156
00:12:14,639 --> 00:12:16,639
Mother, don't go. Mother.

157
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,480
Mother.

158
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:20,159
Mother.

159
00:12:22,879 --> 00:12:23,879
Mother.

160
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,960
Mother.

161
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:29,600
Mother, come back.

162
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:34,960
I'm so cold.

163
00:13:17,399 --> 00:13:18,720
Bu Zhen, don't move.

164
00:13:19,279 --> 00:13:20,279
Bu Zhen?

165
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:22,639
Who is Bu Zhen?

166
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:26,879
Li Shi Si. I'm coming in.

167
00:13:33,279 --> 00:13:34,279
I'll go ahead.

168
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:36,279
Hold on!

169
00:13:36,879 --> 00:13:37,879
Wait!

170
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:44,000
Wait!

171
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:46,360
Stop!

172
00:13:46,759 --> 00:13:48,600
Stop! I have something to tell you!

173
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,559
- Let me warn you. - Me?

174
00:13:50,559 --> 00:13:52,000
From now on, don't wander around the camp.

175
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:54,000
And don't go near Prince Sun's tent.

176
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,960
Why are you acting like this?

177
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,960
Don't come near me!

178
00:13:56,960 --> 00:13:58,360
Do you want to bite me again?

179
00:13:58,679 --> 00:14:00,120
I'm warning you. Don't wander around too much.

180
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,399
Or you'll be sorry!

181
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,320
I really have something to tell you.

182
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,000
I live with Military Strategist Li now.

183
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,840
There's not enough food for both of us.

184
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,679
You have to prepare some food for us.

185
00:14:08,679 --> 00:14:10,720
Why are you telling me that? Tell Military Strategist Li.

186
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,200
- You're eating here? - Yes.

187
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,559
- Here. - Here. Pour him a cup full.

188
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,559
Drink up.

189
00:14:20,879 --> 00:14:21,960
Pour the wine.

190
00:14:26,399 --> 00:14:27,480
Hey!

191
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,480
Why did you follow me?

192
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,720
Military Strategist Li is sick.

193
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,919
Yesterday, he gave me the last remaining food.

194
00:14:31,919 --> 00:14:33,120
We need food.

195
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:35,240
There's a quota for every tent.

196
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:36,720
You've already taken yours.

197
00:14:45,519 --> 00:14:47,200
- You can't take that. - Move!

198
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,240
You...

199
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,080
I'm almost done.

200
00:15:16,440 --> 00:15:17,440
Have a seat.

201
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,200
By the way,

202
00:15:21,639 --> 00:15:24,559
don't the people of Tang like to use this?

203
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:27,279
I made these using a branch.

204
00:15:27,919 --> 00:15:29,440
I hope you like it.

205
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,200
Do as the locals do.

206
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,440
I don't use these anymore.

207
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,960
But I really like your gift.

208
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,440
Thank you.

209
00:15:48,759 --> 00:15:49,960
Etiquette requires reciprocation.

210
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,559
Is there anything you want?

211
00:15:51,879 --> 00:15:52,919
Me?

212
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:58,480
Is Bu Zhen your family?

213
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,720
Do you want to be freed...

214
00:16:02,840 --> 00:16:04,080
and go back to your family?

215
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,279
My clan...

216
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:09,480
has already been invaded by the Ashina Tribe.

217
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,120
They're either dead...

218
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,720
or dispersed already.

219
00:16:14,799 --> 00:16:16,120
I no longer have a family.

220
00:16:18,559 --> 00:16:20,559
So I'm really grateful that you're letting me stay...

221
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,679
by your side.

222
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,559
So we're the same.

223
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:26,120
The same?

224
00:16:28,399 --> 00:16:31,559
Could it be that your family...

225
00:16:32,559 --> 00:16:34,039
My family is also dead.

226
00:16:35,159 --> 00:16:36,440
They were killed by my enemy.

227
00:16:39,879 --> 00:16:41,200
Let's not talk about unhappy things.

228
00:16:41,519 --> 00:16:43,879
Since we met under these circumstances,

229
00:16:43,879 --> 00:16:45,159
this must be fate.

230
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:46,600
From now on,

231
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,200
you can think of me as your family.

232
00:16:50,399 --> 00:16:51,399
Here.

233
00:16:54,159 --> 00:16:55,200
Take the bigger one.

234
00:17:12,759 --> 00:17:13,799
I'm exhausted.

235
00:17:14,170 --> 00:17:15,319
We're almost done.

236
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,799
Let's take a break.

237
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:18,200
That sounds good.

238
00:17:35,519 --> 00:17:37,170
I'm exhausted.

239
00:17:38,279 --> 00:17:39,759
- I'm exhausted. - You're exhausted?

240
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:42,240
Don't you know that we must deliver the goods tomorrow?

241
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:44,170
Have you finished all your work?

242
00:17:44,170 --> 00:17:45,680
If we can't deliver this batch of goods,

243
00:17:45,799 --> 00:17:46,920
get out of here!

244
00:17:48,279 --> 00:17:49,279
Get back to work.

245
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:53,200
Madam Zhang.

246
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:54,440
Don't cause trouble!

247
00:17:58,799 --> 00:18:00,759
Li Le Yan, did you do that on purpose?

248
00:18:00,759 --> 00:18:01,839
Look at what you did.

249
00:18:02,039 --> 00:18:03,240
Scram! Get out of here!

250
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,279
Get her out of here!

251
00:18:04,410 --> 00:18:06,079
- Come on. Hurry up! - Don't...

252
00:18:06,079 --> 00:18:07,170
That's enough.

253
00:18:07,170 --> 00:18:08,240
- Get out. - Stop.

254
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:10,359
- Get out of here. - Get her out of here.

255
00:18:10,599 --> 00:18:11,650
Get out!

256
00:18:11,650 --> 00:18:12,720
- Get out. - Get out!

257
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:15,650
- Is Li Le Yan really stupid? - Indeed.

258
00:18:15,650 --> 00:18:18,079
- Why is she so stupid? - Yes, she's not helping at all.

259
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:41,410
We finally managed to deliver Mr. Hu's order.

260
00:18:41,720 --> 00:18:43,170
Let's all take a break.

261
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:48,359
My neck is so sore.

262
00:18:50,359 --> 00:18:51,759
Why is she still here?

263
00:18:51,759 --> 00:18:54,200
- Yes, she's still here. - Why are you still here?

264
00:18:54,200 --> 00:18:55,480
- That's right. - Madam Chai.

265
00:18:56,359 --> 00:18:57,359
I'm sorry.

266
00:18:59,440 --> 00:19:01,240
Please give me one more chance.

267
00:19:01,559 --> 00:19:02,599
Please.

268
00:19:02,890 --> 00:19:04,440
- Ms. Li. - Why is she still...

269
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:06,410
You're undaunted by repeated setbacks.

270
00:19:06,410 --> 00:19:07,519
Actually,

271
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:09,519
I need someone like you here.

272
00:19:12,039 --> 00:19:13,079
But...

273
00:19:17,599 --> 00:19:19,410
Do you think that after bowing,

274
00:19:19,410 --> 00:19:20,680
I would say that?

275
00:19:21,119 --> 00:19:23,200
You just say some words, and you're able to eat for free here?

276
00:19:23,799 --> 00:19:25,079
Dream on.

277
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:27,599
- That's right. - Later,

278
00:19:27,599 --> 00:19:29,200
I still have to entertain Mr. Hu.

279
00:19:29,599 --> 00:19:31,000
I'm begging you.

280
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,359
Please go.

281
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,960
My shop is too small.

282
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:35,920
Go and make trouble somewhere else.

283
00:19:39,519 --> 00:19:41,119
Are you going to cry?

284
00:19:41,279 --> 00:19:42,650
Look at them.

